            "type": "intro-video",
            "video_src": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/W0CnKcrnoIc?feature=oembed",
            "title": "Bryntum Scheduler Pro Intro"
        },
        {
            "id": "block_ca62340a695d26f1e58162162bd1cb2b",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Task Dependencies",
            "heading": "Link Up Your Tasks",
            "body_html": "<p class=\"p1\">Once your tasks and dependencies are set, the pro-grade scheduling engine handles the rest by:</p> <ul> <li>Arranging tasks based on how they relate and on the rules you’ve set.</li> <li>Auto-shifting downstream tasks whenever you move a leading task.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Once your tasks and dependencies are set, the pro-grade scheduling engine handles the rest by: Arranging tasks based on how they relate and on the rules you’ve set. Auto-shifting downstream tasks whenever you move a leading task.",
            "links": [],
            "ctas": [
                {
                    "text": "See all features",
