        {
            "id": "block_86cff8bcd91213c53bcd78636afc0cd6",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Resource Management",
            "heading": "Don’t Over-Allocate Your Resources",
            "body_html": "<p>Track your team’s workload with a built-in histogram so you can decide faster and more fairly.</p> <ul> <li>Bright red highlights make over-capacity workloads obvious at a glance. <span class=\"s1\">No digging through tables or reports.</span></li> <li>Tweak task assignments to keep the plan balanced.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Track your team’s workload with a built-in histogram so you can decide faster and more fairly. Bright red highlights make over-capacity workloads obvious at a glance. No digging through tables or reports. Tweak task assignments to keep the plan balanced.",
            "links": [],
            "ctas": [
                {
                    "text": "Open demo",
                    "href": "/products/schedulerpro/examples/resourcehistogram",
                    "title": "Open demo"
                }
            ],
            "media": [
                {
                    "kind": "image",
