        {
            "id": "block_78337de647f86a668cc457859b96e116",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Task Editing",
            "heading": "Tailor Task Editing",
            "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bryntum Scheduler Pro also ships with a capable, customisable task editor:</span></p> <ul> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tweak any built-in field and bring your own.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Edit predecessors, successors and constraints.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Show or hide any of the preconfigured fields.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/schedulerpro/examples/calendar-editor/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create and edit multiple calendars</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apply changes live, then roll them back if needed.</span></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Bryntum Scheduler Pro also ships with a capable, customisable task editor: Tweak any built-in field and bring your own. Edit predecessors, successors and constraints. Show or hide any of the preconfigured fields. Create and edit multiple calendars . Apply changes live, then roll them back if needed.",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "Create and edit multiple calendars",
                    "href": "https://bryntum.com/products/schedulerpro/examples/calendar-editor/"
                }
            ],
            "ctas": [
